{"tid":2328042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE〈Eyes Wide Open〉打入告示牌兩百強專輯榜　名次大幅進步創自身新高！","createTime":"2020-12-16T10:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T11:43:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7650ad5dbeb74881f133b74cfbf01ab9ebfd11d","tid":2328042,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_786caef59093774024a24b9090bff4c4/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132369-889174.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_786caef59093774024a24b9090bff4c4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132369-889174.png&h=1d7b54dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早已在韓國和日本大展銷量威力的 TWICE，如今也在美國告示牌上獲得空前的好成績！<br />\n<br />\n根據告示牌預告的榜單，在即將於 19 日更新的告示牌兩百強專輯榜上，TWICE 的第二張錚歸專輯〈Eyes Wide Open〉將拿下第 72 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_08af057431b0b25eeaacb6852ea020c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-16/132369-889175.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_08af057431b0b25eeaacb6852ea020c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-16%2F132369-889175.jpg&h=bfa8abd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 在去年出道將滿四週年前發行了第九張迷你專輯〈MORE &amp; MORE〉，當時才首度打入兩百強專輯榜這座具有代表性的音樂榜單。而今年她們在韓國、日本的專輯總銷量早已突破一千萬大關，〈Eyes Wide Open〉還在發行七週後打入兩百強專輯榜，並展現了大幅進步，讓人對她們未來的表現更加期待。<br />\n<br />\n除了登上兩百強專輯榜外，TWICE 也分別在世界專輯榜、綜合專輯銷量榜和 Artist 100 榜上拿下第 2、12 及 73 名。另一方面，本月 18 日 TWICE 還將推出新歌 &ldquo;CRY FOR ME&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"9f9d77becb3e48198e93fef8149fda16d024ac87","tid":2328042,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"好厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1f0bdc1bca2e43d332171e6a4dcf8d9910df29","tid":2328042,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"我TWICE又然 我老婆強勢回歸後必創新高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fa9b286a27b2b7ea2f877491770317cd80c0a5","tid":2328042,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"我嘅Mina真係好正"},{"pid":"068643569e27a800b9d7b697e09fa151950cfd94","tid":2328042,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"84fa9b286a27b2b7ea2f877491770317cd80c0a5","tid":2328042,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"我嘅Mina真係好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"Mina is once<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}